      "created": "2021-12-01T05:57:11.682+0000",
      "description": "This Jira proposes to add support for accepting request from disributed sources for putting nodes in decomissioning state.\u00a0\r\n\r\nIt proposes to add configurable provider and consumer class interface in nodemanager. NM can receive request to put node in decomissioning from any distributed sources using the provider class implementation and consumer classes can utilize it to set node status.\u00a0\r\n\r\nCorresponding changes will be done at RM side to update node staate while update event is called at DecomissioningNodesWatcher.",
